# the Repeat keyword
let start simple ;-)  
The easiest way to do an action repeatidly in Gwion is, ... the **repeat** keyword!

## Basic example

```gwion,editable
repeat(3)
   <<< "Hello, world!" >>>;
```  


## Block example

of course this also works with a block code.

```gwion,editable
repeat(3) {
   maybe ? "You" : "Me" => var string s;
   <<< "Hello, ", s, "!" >>>;
}
```  
